RICF model summary

Source: R/semPaths.R
summary.RICF.Rd

Generate a summary for a RICF solver similar to lavaan-formatted summary

# S3 method for RICF
summary(object, ...)

Arguments

object

A RICF fitted model object.
...

Currently ignored.

Value

Shown the lavaan-formatted summary to console

See also

SEMrun.

Author

Mario Grassi mario.grassi@unipv.it

Examples

sem0 <- SEMrun(sachs$graph, log(sachs$pkc), algo = "ricf")

#> RICF solver ended normally after 2 iterations 
#> 
#> deviance/df: 66.93929  srmr: 0.0894731 
#> 
summary(sem0$fit)
